name: Super Harvest
description: In Super Harvest your goal is the collect as many crops as you can, there is no way to die or time limit, you just play till you feel bored, I first made an other project for Ludum dare 52 yesterday but I had to many things to do, so I made this game 2 - 3 hours, I don't feel proud of it but its my first game jam and I don't really care
